,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T17:37:25.000Z","msg":"鋪主吸乾佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd210e61e1006493c6c09739402cb2dcb74e278d","tid":1994942,"uid":83989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T17:57:34.000Z","msg":"越潮好耐了聽日落街幫襯"},{"pid":"9d787ddef999bbf2fa5fc1377b99b66e59979799","tid":1994942,"uid":215164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T18:10:16.000Z","msg":"越潮好食 <br />\n不過睇wolipay啲留言話唔覺黃<br />\n諗返又好似真係去親都睇cctvb<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa7c34bc4558f18681ebae0c99fca5ba69d19bfd","tid":1994942,"uid":96708,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T19:48:50.000Z","msg":"有無諗過明明中環cafe應該好易做，點解仲要告急<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4a1293e1605df5434fa53141b29e8b99063b9ba","tid":1994942,"uid":161417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a6b19663960974105b7ccd3954e470410af44e85","tid":1994942,"uid":85774,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T01:15:51.000Z","msg":"第一間個老闆都幾有米 22歲投資過百萬"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T19:55:40.000Z","msg":"唔算太高，其實開親食店都要依個價"},{"pid":"ce28b808ce52e16a0ca3c0352d3a203ee5a5d2b3","tid":1994942,"uid":198804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fa7c34bc4558f18681ebae0c99fca5ba69d19bfd","tid":1994942,"uid":96708,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T19:48:50.000Z","msg":"有無諗過明明中環cafe應該好易做，點解仲要告急<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T20:21:03.000Z","msg":"中上環/西區啲cafe真係永遠旺場<br />\n之前最少人出街果排啲cafe都仲坐到6-7成滿<br />\n佢一日得$300生意，即係賣得6杯咖啡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec9790ae5b8b070eb89785bc5d053e0297082250","tid":1994942,"uid":212646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T20:33:34.000Z","msg":"呢間係cafe/bar黎<br />\n日頭唔敢講，夜晚我估得假期前一晚生意先叫好啲<br />\nPeel street經常有狗查<br />\n好多鬼而家都廢事去<br />\n反而去撚哂西營盤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無耐前去過俾左少少tips，睇得出老板嗰下真係開心<br />\n無刻意講啲咩<br />\n我相信老板知道四海之內皆有手足"}]}